
Update a site.

See: https://google.aip.dev/134 (Standard methods: Update).

USAGE
  update-site <command>

ARGUMENT FLAGS
  --site.name                    string      Resource name of the site
  --site.display-name       [R]  string      Display name of the site
  --site.lat-lng.latitude        double      Latitude in degrees
  --site.lat-lng.longitude       double      Longitude in degrees
  --update-mask                  field-mask  List of fields to be updated

CONNECTION FLAGS
  --address        string  Connect to address
  --force-trace    bool    Enable forced Google Cloud Trace header
  --insecure       bool    Make insecure connection (only on localhost)
  --token          string  Authenticate with a bearer token

OTHER FLAGS
  -f  --from-file    string  path to a JSON file containing the request payload
  -h  --help         bool    Show help for command
  -v  --verbose      bool    Enable verbose output
